{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><p>&#13;\n\t\t\t日本氣象廳表示，日本東北部海域發生7.4級地震，當局已發布海嘯警報。<br/>&#13;\n<br/>&#13;\n當地傳媒報道，預計高達3米的海嘯，將抵達北海道、岩手縣。\t\t</p>&#13;\n\t\t&#13;\n\t\t<h2>日本東北部海域發生7.4級地震 已發出海嘯警報</h2><p>2026-04-20 HKT 16:11</p> &#13;\n    &#13;\n    \t&#13;\n\t&#13;\n\t<p><ref href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1851758-20260420.htm\" target=\"blank\" onclick=\"dcsMultiTrack('DCS.dcsuri','https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1851758-20260420.htm?share=facebook','WT.dl','99','WT.cg_n','#rthknews','WT.cg_s','Share');\"><img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/frontend_images/social_icons/fc-webicon-facebook-s.png\" alt=\"facebook\" title=\"facebook\">&#13;\n\t\t\t</ref></p><img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/frontend_images/social_icons/fc-webicon-facebook-s.png\" alt=\"facebook\" title=\"facebook\"><p><ref target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1851758-20260420.htm&amp;text=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9D%B1%E5%8C%97%E9%83%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F7.4%E7%B4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E3%80%80%E5%B7%B2%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%B7%E5%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%A0%B1\" onclick=\"dcsMultiTrack('DCS.dcsuri','https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1851758-20260420.htm?share=twitter','WT.dl','99','WT.cg_n','#rthknews','WT.cg_s','Share');\" class=\"twitter-share-button\" data-count=\"horizontal\"><img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/frontend_images/social_icons/fc-webicon-twitter-s.png\" alt=\"twitter\" title=\"twitter\">&#13;\n\t\t\t</ref></p><img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/frontend_images/social_icons/fc-webicon-twitter-s.png\" alt=\"twitter\" title=\"twitter\"><p><img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/frontend_images/images/st_tyneo/RTHK-logo.png\" alt=\"香港電台網站 - 中文新聞\"></p></body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-20T09:45:18.620828+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":108,"images":5,"source":"RTHK 國際","fallback":"none"}}